  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Describable, Filterable, Sortable

    public class JUnitQuickcheck
extends BlockJUnit4ClassRunner

    JUnit test runner for junit-quickcheck property-based tests.

    When this runner runs a given test class, it regards only public instance methods with a return type of void that are marked with either the Property annotation or the org.junit.Test annotation.

    This runner honors Rule, Before, After, BeforeClass, and AfterClass. Their execution is wrapped around the verification of a property or execution of a test in the expected order.
